#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag3.1:4.1"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"aggikabhāradvājattheragāthā (bj)\" id=\"note148\">3.1 Aṅgaṇikabhāradvājattheragāthā</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc219"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts219"></a><a class="pts" id="pts29"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.1:5.1"
msgid "“Ayoni suddhimanvesaṃ,"
msgstr "Seeking purity the wrong way,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:5.2"
msgid "aggiṃ paricariṃ vane;"
msgstr "I served the sacred fire in a grove."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:5.3"
msgid "Suddhimaggaṃ ajānanto,"
msgstr "Not knowing the path to purity,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:5.4"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"akāsiṃ aparaṃ tapaṃ (s2, s3) | akāsiṃ amataṃ tapaṃ (mr)\" id=\"note149\">akāsiṃ amaraṃ tapaṃ</span>."
msgstr "I mortified my flesh in search of immortality."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc220"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts220"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.1:6.1"
msgid "Taṃ sukhena sukhaṃ laddhaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ve gained this happiness by means of happiness:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:6.2"
msgid "passa dhammasudhammataṃ;"
msgstr "See the excellence of the Dhamma!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:6.3"
msgid "Tisso vijjā anuppattā,"
msgstr "I’ve attained the three knowledges,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:6.4"
msgid "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanaṃ."
msgstr "And fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc221"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts221"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.1:7.1"
msgid "Brahmabandhu pure āsiṃ,"
msgstr "In the past I was related to Brahmā,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:7.2"
msgid "idāni khomhi brāhmaṇo;"
msgstr "But now I’m really a brahmin:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:7.3"
msgid "Tevijjo <span class=\"var\" title=\"nahātako (bj)\" id=\"note150\">nhātako</span> camhi,"
msgstr "I have the three knowledges, I’m cleansed,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.1:7.4"
msgid "sottiyo camhi vedagū”ti."
msgstr "I’m an initiate, and I’m accomplished in sacred knowledge."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
